OL,3,CAt least 172 mothers killed by sons in
OL,4,Cpast 15 years, report reveals
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Jamel Smith
OL,8,FAt least 172 mothers have been killed
OL,9,Fby their sons in the past 15 years,
OL,10,Fand children have witnessed their
OL,11,Fmother being murdered in more than 120
OL,12,Fcases, a new report reveals.
OL,14,FThe Femicide Census, a database
OL,15,Ftracking women killed in the UK, has
OL,16,Frecorded over 2,000 cases of women
OL,17,Fmurdered by men convicted in court
OL,18,Fsince 2009.
