OL,3,CAt least 172 mothers killed by sons in
OL,4,Cpast 15 years, report reveals
OL,6,FKaren Ingala Smith, co-founder of the
OL,7,Forganisation, told ITV News: "We're
OL,8,Fcalling this an issue of state
OL,9,Ffailure, the patterns have been clear
OL,10,Ffor a long time."
OL,12,FShe added that mental health services
OL,13,Fhave failed to carry out proper risk
OL,14,Fassessments for male violence.
OL,16,F"Nobody's been asking the question
OL,17,Fabout what's going on, why hasn't
OL,18,Fthere been an emergency call for risk
OL,19,Fassessments for men who are abusive to
OL,20,Ffemale relatives?" she said.
