OL,3,CAt least 172 mothers killed by sons in
OL,4,Cpast 15 years, report reveals
OL,6,FThe report also highlights the
OL,7,Fsentences handed down to men convicted
OL,8,Fof killing women.
OL,10,FWhile 60% were found guilty of murder,
OL,11,F22% were convicted of manslaughter on
OL,12,Fthe grounds of diminished
OL,13,Fresponsibility or culpable homicide,
OL,14,Fand 12% took their own lives.
OL,16,FThe shortest sentence served for
OL,17,Fmurder was nine years, while the
OL,18,Flongest was 47.
OL,20,FOnly 20 convicted murderers - just 1%
OL,21,F- received whole-life terms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
