OL,6,FMs Smith urged politicians to take "a
OL,7,Fvery broad approach" in tackling
OL,8,Ffemicide.
OL,10,FShe said British society needs to
OL,11,Fexamine how individuals form views on
OL,12,Fsex and gender, as well as the roles
OL,13,Fof socialisation, family structures,
OL,14,Fhousing, immigration, pornography, and
OL,15,Fprostitution.
OL,17,F"We're (Britain) focused mainly on law
OL,18,Fand policing and that's necessary and
OL,19,Fwe know that there's such a lot of
OL,20,Fchange needed.
